  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/0acb24ec3fd1bf323a09305269ae3769.poster.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/0acb24ec3fd1bf323a09305269ae3769.webm?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/0acb24ec3fd1bf323a09305269ae3769.mp4?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Zodiac System is breaking. Only you can fix it.<br><br>Play as a young engineer named Leo and fight deadly robots on a quest to save your home planet from the sinister plans of The Stranger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/4087cd5aea190923737316fd27a39580.poster.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/4087cd5aea190923737316fd27a39580.webm?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/4087cd5aea190923737316fd27a39580.mp4?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Boss fights only. Master a fluid and satisfying combat system to take down 10 increasingly difficult bosses.<br><br>Slash, shoot, and dodge your way to victory. Land melee attacks to replenish your ammo, then unleash a barrage of long-range attacks at your enemy. This short-range, long-range system infuses boss fights with a steady rhythm and keeps you in the action.<br><br>Full animation canceling and freedom of movement means you'll never lose to a cheap shot. Learn your enemy's movements and defeat them through skill.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/28bd9fbda5cfcaa703e2c22ec64869af.poster.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/28bd9fbda5cfcaa703e2c22ec64869af.webm?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/28bd9fbda5cfcaa703e2c22ec64869af.mp4?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Leo's planet is a robot-powered utopia, but not all is as it seems.<br><br>Talk with locals and discover the source of the Zodiac System's malfunctions.<br><br>Get to know a colorful and diverse cast of characters brought to life through hand-drawn portraits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/4ec6539da709b2f56566f71f7536a285.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/95ae58fb75c9c69843535d6b173f291b.poster.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/95ae58fb75c9c69843535d6b173f291b.webm?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/95ae58fb75c9c69843535d6b173f291b.mp4?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join Leo on a globe-trotting adventure across Verge.<br><br>Treat your eyes to a beautiful pixel-art world, calling back to the classics of the 16-bit era.<br><br>Tune your ears to over a dozen tracks of pulse-pounding and nostalgia-inducing original music.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2>- 10 unique and challenging boss encounters<br>- A compelling sci-fi story about the cost of progress<br>- Responsive and fluid combat<br>- Pixel-perfect art style and hand-drawn characters<br>- Completely original soundtrack",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/0acb24ec3fd1bf323a09305269ae3769.poster.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/0acb24ec3fd1bf323a09305269ae3769.webm?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/0acb24ec3fd1bf323a09305269ae3769.mp4?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Zodiac System is breaking. Only you can fix it.<br><br>Play as a young engineer named Leo and fight deadly robots on a quest to save your home planet from the sinister plans of The Stranger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/4087cd5aea190923737316fd27a39580.poster.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/4087cd5aea190923737316fd27a39580.webm?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/4087cd5aea190923737316fd27a39580.mp4?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Boss fights only. Master a fluid and satisfying combat system to take down 10 increasingly difficult bosses.<br><br>Slash, shoot, and dodge your way to victory. Land melee attacks to replenish your ammo, then unleash a barrage of long-range attacks at your enemy. This short-range, long-range system infuses boss fights with a steady rhythm and keeps you in the action.<br><br>Full animation canceling and freedom of movement means you'll never lose to a cheap shot. Learn your enemy's movements and defeat them through skill.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/28bd9fbda5cfcaa703e2c22ec64869af.poster.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/28bd9fbda5cfcaa703e2c22ec64869af.webm?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/28bd9fbda5cfcaa703e2c22ec64869af.mp4?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Leo's planet is a robot-powered utopia, but not all is as it seems.<br><br>Talk with locals and discover the source of the Zodiac System's malfunctions.<br><br>Get to know a colorful and diverse cast of characters brought to life through hand-drawn portraits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/4ec6539da709b2f56566f71f7536a285.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/95ae58fb75c9c69843535d6b173f291b.poster.avif?t=1772421794\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/95ae58fb75c9c69843535d6b173f291b.webm?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403880/extras/95ae58fb75c9c69843535d6b173f291b.mp4?t=1772421794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join Leo on a globe-trotting adventure across Verge.<br><br>Treat your eyes to a beautiful pixel-art world, calling back to the classics of the 16-bit era.<br><br>Tune your ears to over a dozen tracks of pulse-pounding and nostalgia-inducing original music.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2>- 10 unique and challenging boss encounters<br>- A compelling sci-fi story about the cost of progress<br>- Responsive and fluid combat<br>- Pixel-perfect art style and hand-drawn characters<br>- Completely original soundtrack",
